Calls a cacheable function or method (or not if there is already a cache for it)  Arguments of this method are read with func_get_args. So it doesn't appear in the function definition. Synopsis : call('functionName', $arg1, $arg2, ...) (arg1, arg2... are arguments of 'functionName') 
